rows.label: bf05060100_0030
rows.name:
Rumor had it that Superbia were
conducting an excavation there.

rows.label: bf05060100_0040
rows.name: So I thought I should check it out, and, er...

rows.label: bf05060100_0050
rows.name: It's changed a lot, but this shape...

rows.label: bf05060100_0060
rows.name: That's a Judicium Divine Beast weapon.

rows.label: bf05060100_0090
rows.name:
Right. It was destroyed.
A casualty of the Aegis War.

rows.label: bf05060100_0100
rows.name: And it's where the Flesh Eaters were created.

rows.label: bf05060100_0130
rows.name: If it is a threat to us, it should be destroyed.

rows.label: bf05060100_0140
rows.name: ...Or, we could make use of it.

rows.label: bf05060100_0150
rows.name: Damn it all, I can't believe this!

rows.label: bf05060100_0160
rows.name:
Hello Benkei.
And a very good day to you too.

rows.label: bf05060100_0190
rows.name: We got the goods. No problem.

rows.label: bf05060100_0230
rows.name:
Long story short, we had to make
a run for it.

rows.label: bf05060100_0240
rows.name:
And you're sure it wasn't your
ether field that was disturbed?

rows.label: bf05060100_0270
rows.name: It's Kasumi. No doubt about it.

rows.label: bf05060100_0300
rows.name: Satahiko, how goes the work on the Marsanes?

rows.label: bf05060100_0320
rows.name:
It'll take a little longer than I
thought, but we'll get there.

rows.label: bf05060100_0330
rows.name: And Yoshitsune - where is the Holy Grail right now?

rows.label: bf05060100_0350
rows.name: She's on the move, maybe on a ship.

rows.label: bf05060100_0390
rows.name:
Temperantia.
To buy us some time.

rows.label: bf05060100_0410
rows.name: If that man gets into her head...

rows.label: bf05060100_0440
rows.name: In fact, she'll be a big help to us.

rows.label: bf05060100_0450
rows.name:
After all, only an Holy Grail
can open up the path to the World Tree.

rows.label: bf05060100_0460
rows.name:
Metsu, there's a lot of work to be
done on what we got from the Guild.

rows.label: bf05060100_0470
rows.name: You guys, stay here and help Satahiko.

rows.label: bf05060100_0500
rows.name: Very well. Take care of yourself.
